abstract: Floyd Norris Off The Charts column examines import statistics in several euro zone countries; notes that while nearly all are in renewed decline due to slowing economies, some countries are doing better than others.
snippet: Statistics on imports help show which countries in Europe are doing well, which are showing signs of stress but still growing and which have major problems.
lead_paragraph: Statistics on imports help show which countries in Europe are doing well, which are showing signs of stress but still growing and which have major problems.

headline.main: Europe’s Consumers Are Pointing the Way Down
